{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"IntersectionObserver.root","mdn_url":"/ko/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserver/root","locale":"ko","native":"한국어","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Intersection_Observer_API\">Intersection Observer API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserver\"><code>IntersectionObserver</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserver/IntersectionObserver\"><code>IntersectionObserver()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Properties</summary><ol><li><em><code>root</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserver/rootMargin\"><code>rootMargin</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserver/thresholds\"><code>thresholds</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methods</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserver/disconnect\"><code>disconnect()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserver/observe\"><code>observe()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserver/takeRecords\"><code>takeRecords()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserver/unobserve\"><code>unobserve()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for Intersection Observer API</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserverEntry\"><code>IntersectionObserverEntry</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/indexedDB\"><code>indexedDB</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserver\"><code>IntersectionObserver</code></a> 인터페이스의 <strong><code>root</code></strong> 읽기 전용 속성은 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/bounding_box\">바운딩 박스 <small>(en-US)</small></a>를 주시 대상의 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Glossary/Viewport\">뷰포트</a>로 취급하는 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a> 또는 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a>를 나타냅니다.</p>\n<p><code>root</code>가 <code>null</code>이면 문서의 실제 뷰포트 바운딩 박스를 사용합니다.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"값","title":"값","isH3":false,"content":"<p>대상 요소가 얼마나 보이는지 판별할 때, 그 뷰포트 경계로서 바운딩 박스를 가져오는 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a> 또는 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a> 객체입니다.</p>\n<p>이 뷰포트 경계에 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserver/IntersectionObserver\" title=\"IntersectionObserver()\"><code>IntersectionObserver()</code></a> 생성자로 제공한 여백 설정을 적용한 직사각형 영역과, 대상 요소의 경계에서 그 위에 겹치는 다른 요소의 경계를 뺐을 때의 직사각형 영역을 대상 요소에서 볼 수 있는 영역으로 취급합니다.</p>\n<p><code>root</code>가 <code>null</code>이면 현재 문서를 루트로, 그 뷰포트(문서에서 지금 보이는 영역)를 루트 경계로 사용합니다.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"예제","title":"예제","isH3":false,"content":"<p>CSS <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/CSS/border\"><code>border</code></a> 속성을 사용해서 교차 감지기의 루트 요소에 2픽셀 초록색 테두리를 추가하는 예제입니다.</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>observer<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>root<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>border <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"2px solid #44aa44\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"명세","id":"명세","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/IntersectionObserver/#dom-intersectionobserver-root","title":"Intersection Observer"}],"query":"api.IntersectionObserver.root"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"브라우저 호환성","id":"브라우저_호환성","isH3":false,"query":"api.IntersectionObserver.root","dataURL":"/ko/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserver/root/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"같이_보기","title":"같이 보기","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Intersection_Observer_API/Timing_element_visibility\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Intersection Observer API로 요소가 보여진 시간 측정하기 (en-US)</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"값","id":"값"},{"text":"예제","id":"예제"},{"text":"명세","id":"명세"},{"text":"브라우저 호환성","id":"브라우저_호환성"},{"text":"같이 보기","id":"같이_보기"}],"summary":"IntersectionObserver 인터페이스의 root 읽기 전용 속성은 바운딩 박스 (en-US)를 주시 대상의 뷰포트로 취급하는 Element 또는 Document를 나타냅니다.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"IntersectionObserver.root","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"IntersectionObserver.root","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"IntersectionObserver.root","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ko/web/api/intersectionobserver/root","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ko/web/api/intersectionobserver/root/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web","title":"개발자를 위한 웹 기술"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserver","title":"IntersectionObserver"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserver/root","title":"IntersectionObserver.root"}],"pageTitle":"IntersectionObserver.root - Web API | MDN